199
00:20:40,622 --> 00:20:43,067
And all of a sudden, I go, "Whoa."

200
00:20:43,067 --> 00:20:46,510
I see, you know, one of them standing there and just transfixed. 

201
00:20:46,512 --> 00:20:50,900
And I say, "Theresa, take him away."

