210
00:21:52,533 --> 00:21:57,033
And so I said, "Well, maybe they're right back to where they were last night."

211
00:21:57,183 --> 00:22:00,583
So we just turned and went towards the center.

212
00:22:02,007 --> 00:22:07,607
<i>As Dallaire looked for the extremist leaders, the prime minister's house was surrounded by Rwandan troops.</i>

213
00:22:09,632 --> 00:22:15,202
