214
00:22:17,004 --> 00:22:21,004
<i>The prime minister called her neighbor, American diplomat Joyce Leader.</i>

215
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:24,230
JOYCE LEADER: 
About 8:30 in the morning,

216
00:22:25,284 --> 00:22:28,984
she called and asked if she could come and hide in my house.

217
00:22:29,404 --> 00:22:32,710
- The prime minister?
- The prime minister. And...

218



219
00:22:34,765 --> 00:22:40,015
I didn't give it very much thought, and I said yes,

220
00:22:41,005 --> 00:22:47,105
but then when the Ghanaian peacekeeper who was guarding her --

221
00:22:50,004 --> 00:22:53,894
he must have put a ladder up on her side of the fence,

222
00:22:54,079 --> 00:22:59,971
and he came up above the -- he raised his head above the fence, and there were shots fired,

223
00:22:59,071 --> 00:23:00,600
