238
00:24:22,009 --> 00:24:28,879
<i>General Dallaire hadn't heard of the attack, but he'd learned the extremist leadership was meeting at army headquarters.</i>

239
00:24:30,005 --> 00:24:35,695
<i>As he approached, Dallaire caught a glimpse of his soldiers inside the Army compound, lying in the dirt.</i>

240
00:24:39,073 --> 00:24:51,273
Gen. ROMEO DALLAIRE: 
And at the gate, as we went by, I saw two soldiers in the Belgian uniform lying on the ground about 50-odd meters inside-- inside the camp.

241
00:24:52,877 --> 00:25:00,973
And so your whole life is dependent on those nano-seconds 
